{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "operations", "channel": "warehouse_management", "user": "Sophie Tran", "message": "We've been getting feedback about the lack of certain items in the store. Let's schedule a meeting to discuss restocking plans for next week.", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "operations", "channel": "warehouse_management", "user": "John Lee", "message": "Agreed, Sophie. Can you prepare an inventory report to discuss during the meeting? It would be helpful to know the current status.", "created_at": 1620500100000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "training", "channel": "knowledge_sharing", "user": "Linda Choi", "message": "Just a reminder that the next HR training session is next Tuesday. All managers should attend the session to understand the new policies.", "created_at": 1620500200000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "operations", "channel": "warehouse_management", "user": "Sophie Tran", "message": "John, I'll compile the inventory report by end of day today. We can review it first thing in the morning.", "created_at": 1620500300000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "training", "channel": "knowledge_sharing", "user": "John Lee", "message": "Thanks for the reminder, Linda. I'll also be discussing some strategic objectives for the coming quarter during the session.", "created_at": 1620500400000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "operations", "channel": "warehouse_management", "user": "Linda Choi", "message": "Sophie, would you be able to share that inventory report with me as well? It would be helpful for our HR planning.", "created_at": 1620500500000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "training", "channel": "knowledge_sharing", "user": "Sophie Tran", "message": "Absolutely, Linda. I'll make sure to include you in the distribution list.", "created_at": 1620500600000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "training", "channel": "knowledge_sharing", "user": "Sophie Tran", "message": "Hello team, just a quick update on our training programs for 2025. We had a total of 100 training programs this year, of which 25 programs were specifically designed to encourage a culture of knowledge-sharing among our employees. That's 25% of our total training initiatives focused on fostering knowledge sharing. Let's keep up the good work in building a strong culture of learning and collaboration!", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
